		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			This spell does a maximum of<BR>
28pts for 3 &quot;Ticks&quot; in a radius area around the target.<BR>
The max damage on this spell is 84 pts<BR>
But it seems to be resisted very often.<BR>
Also the main effect of rain spells is to cause the Monsters to jump the wizard casting the spell.<BR>
Also the speed and recovery time on this spell is slow.  A very poor choice of spell except in a very select situation.<BR>
<BR>
-Eldrid<BR>

			</font>
	
