			Even at level 14, this spell is still quite poor. If you manage to affect 3 creatures, you get a damage/mana ratio hardly better than a Shock spell (28x3/62=1.35) and it seems it gets resisted much more. No bonus at all for taking the risk of annoying several creatures at once. Column of Frost is better (but works differently) if you want an AE spell.
