		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			My experience with Firestorm and Frost Spiral<BR>
of Al Kabar (12th lvl spells) is it hits 3 times... period.  <BR>
This could be the same MOB 3 times or 3 different MOBS once each <BR>
or some combination thereof...  At first I thought this was because <BR>
I just got the spell and with more casting it would improve... then I <BR>
figured as I leveled up it would improve... neither of which is the case.<BR>
despite the spell description you hit at most 3 times regardless of <BR>
how many MOBs are in the Area of Effect.  I have casted this spell a LOT<BR>
of times and the results have not changed.  It may change as I level up<BR>
but it hasn't yet... no more money or effort spent getting AOE spells for me.<BR>
<BR>
Do not waste you money on this spell or Frost Spiral.  Stick with Shock of Lightning.<BR>
<BR>
This only pertains to Wiz AOE spells through 12th lvl.<BR>
<BR>
Orasis 15th lvl Wiz
			</font>
	
