			This was printed somewhere else on the website, but I'll post it here for the wizards out there.  The number of times this spell and all rain-based spells hit depends on the number of mobs it's hitting.  If you're hitting one mob, it hits three times.  Two mobs will hit twice each.  Three or four mobs will hit once each.
